{"type": "article", "id": 7630, "title": "Celia Torvisco 巧妙开关电灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-23T07:06:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234830BYHK3AmMNQGtlbkv.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tCelia Torvisco 推出的这一款灯有一个非常巧妙的开关，两根绳子分别是两根导电线，只要把绳子两端系在一起就可以点亮电灯，而当结解开便可以关掉电灯。系在一起的绳子也可以挂在各种不同需要的地方，美观和实用兼备。这款灯有白色，黑色，蓝黑等颜色可选，不过目前现在还没开卖。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234827tTWJZuH1M7mlDzx3.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.85452323\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052348285PFB3e2z4fMgHNp0.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.8801956\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234829e2WH4y70UM8v6hrZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.81662592\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052348292L18RgQU9vHrGzw6.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.7591687\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234829BsHcZdg4LMDu5mJh.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.68826406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234830mnXuIViPb319w0ya.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"